# animate — man, woman, robot kinds
# Lowercase first keyword: treated as common noun, article applied.
# Uppercase first keyword: has proper, printed without article.

room Room "A room."

    man butler "A stiff-backed butler."

    woman Lady Gaga "The one and only."

    robot cleaner "A humming cleaner."

test "default"
    look. "Lady Gaga"
    look. Not "a Lady Gaga"
    look. "a butler"
    take butler. "would care for that"
    take Lady Gaga. "would care for that"
